divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: at about 6:10pm an oval-shaped craft flew in overhead from the east. had a white light in the front and back, and colored flashing lights on the sides. it paused for about 30 seconds above us before speeding off faster than anything i ve ever seen before while making a loud luuueeeeee noise. dogs in the neighborhood began barking insanely and i got a headache. the sky was clear and it sped off to the northwest.
